short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that allows you to import your Musi playlists into YouTube or download them as an archive.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With a simple to use interface, you can easily view your library from your backup code and either import it into YouTube, or download the contents as a file, forever preserving your music. The contents of each playlist are preserved in their order, except for deleted tracks, providing a seamless experience.

The source code for this extension is fully available at https://github.com/SaturnKai/MusiArchiver.
